OK then, let’s not waste another minute, and get talking about the gold standard.

00:01:07.675 --> 00:01:15.315
If you watched Donald Duck cartoons as a child, you might remember Donald’s uncle, Scrooge McDuck.

00:01:15.735 --> 00:01:20.235
He is an extremely rich duck and spends his days

00:01:20.555 --> 00:01:24.425
thinking about his money and ways he can make more of it.

